@optional {metrics: [str] # List that contains the metrics that you want to retrieve for the associated data series. If you don't set this parameter, this resource returns data series for all Coll Stats Latency metrics., start: str(date-time) # Date and time when MongoDB Cloud begins reporting the metrics. This parameter expresses its value in the ISO 8601 timestamp format in UTC. Include this parameter when you do not set **period**., end: str(date-time) # Date and time when MongoDB Cloud stops reporting the metrics. This parameter expresses its value in the ISO 8601 timestamp format in UTC. Include this parameter when you do not set **period**., period: str # Duration over which Atlas reports the metrics. This parameter expresses its value in the ISO 8601 duration format in UTC. Include this parameter when you do not set **start** and **end**.}
